	#' This function returns a dataframe or json object of EasyIEPRunHistories
	#' @param fieldNames A TRUE or FALSE value determining whether or not to return the field for the given object. Defaults to FALSE for all return fields which, for convenience, returns all fields for the object.
	#' @param fieldPaths Fields from other objects with 'Many to One' or 'One to One' relationships to the given object set to TRUE or FALSE. Run getSchemaForObject('EasyIEPRunHistory') to get more field paths.
